abstract: Brooke Henderson takes one-stroke lead with six-under-par 65 at North Texas LPGA Shootout.
lead_paragraph: Brooke Henderson shot a six-under-par 65 in the North Texas Shootout in Irving, giving her a one-stroke lead over Inbee Park and Juli Inkster.

headline.main: Brooke Henderson in Lead at North Texas Shootout
